    public final class HomeView
extends HomeComponents
implements java.util.Observer, IHomeOperations
    This class contains all implementation about the UI. Implements a behavioral of the view and a observer to keep updated when model is changed.
    Author:
    BRKsCosta and danielcordeiro
    See Also:
